{"tid":727400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普: 歐盟與中國一樣壞","createTime":"2018-07-03T03:56:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T04:18:50.000Z","uid":134071,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3a473ce9fc591248d138388ae66907d383019dd7","tid":727400,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T03:56:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0%E7%81%AB%E5%BB%B6%E7%87%92-%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%8A%A8%E6%93%8A%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E8%88%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E6%A8%A3%E5%A3%9E-005909480.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25BF%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%2588%25B0%25E7%2581%25AB%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E7%2587%2592-%25E5%25B7%259D%25E6%2599%25AE%25E6%258A%25A8%25E6%2593%258A%25E6%25AD%2590%25E7%259B%259F%25E8%2588%2587%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E6%25A8%25A3%25E5%25A3%259E-005909480.html&d=wWJOMiaAdzgtWeCRBVsiukkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=af6b47b8\" target=\"_blank\">http://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E6%88%B0%E7%81%AB%E5%BB%B6%E7%87%92-%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E6%8A%A8%E6%93%8A%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E8%88%87%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E6%A8%A3%E5%A3%9E-005909480.html</a></span><br />\n<br />\n貿易戰火延燒 川普抨擊歐盟與中國一樣壞<br />\n新頭殼newtalk |洪翠蓮 綜合報導<br />\n2018年7月2日 上午8:59<br />\n<br />\n[新頭殼newtalk] 美國總統川普（Donald Trump）決定要與歐盟撕破臉了？在歐盟上週決定對美國波本威士忌、牛仔褲與電動單車等指標性商品課徵報復性關稅後，<strong>川普不但揚言要對來自歐盟的進口汽車課徵關稅，也在1日接受電視台訪問時砲轟歐盟「與中國一樣，都是差勁的貿易對手，只是規模比較小而已」。</strong><br />\n<br />\n川普上任以來，頻頻點燃貿易戰火，雖然他試圖與中國國家主席習近平建立良好關係，但對鋼鐵與鋁關稅的針鋒相對，爭吵已經擴大到包括歐盟、加拿大和墨西哥，川普政府拒絕提供關稅豁免，導致歐盟的報復措施，而加拿大也在週日宣布對美國金屬關稅採取報復措施，40多個美國鋼鐵產品的關稅將達到25%。<br />\n<br />\n川普在福斯新聞網周日節目《Sunday Morning Futures》中，大力抨擊歐盟對美國貿易的不公平。他批評「歐盟可能與中國一樣差勁，只是規模比較小一點」。他指出，歐盟派出「梅賽德斯－賓士」（汽車品牌），而美國卻不能進口汽車到歐盟，「他們（歐盟）不要我們的農產品，我們沒有保護農夫，但他們有」。<br />\n<br />\n川普強調他喜歡歐盟的國家，包括德國、蘇格蘭等，但歐盟很不公平地對待美國。對於北美洲的貿易夥伴──加拿大、墨西哥，川普則表示，美方仍與2國重新談判北美自由貿易協定，他希望協議能更公平，會留到11月中期選舉後才簽署協定。<br />\n<br />\n至於被抨擊對中國態度軟化，川普否認，強硬表示如果不能與中國達成協議，可能會向對方加徵更多關稅。"},{"pid":"ac7db3a0e8c3468ae4eaf9cf11546aaae7ce21a5","tid":727400,"uid":156652,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T03:57:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/115707_16375df3b4dee56b4438f164cb720722.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F115707_16375df3b4dee56b4438f164cb720722.gif&h=6103e847&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c186a6571943e929df8fbbd23f8bdccbb7f7344","tid":727400,"uid":137248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T04:06:33.000Z","msg":"侵侵又撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da3fc423be67fe6d11be56d3e5f9c7eb64e2b55f","tid":727400,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T01:17:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c9e019ab50d04cf22a9412b09a7652d1807c8eb","tid":727400,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c186a6571943e929df8fbbd23f8bdccbb7f7344","tid":727400,"uid":137248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T04:06:33.000Z","msg":"侵侵又撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T02:44:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45061b6ac942ef61d9c5d663f8205bfbd9386a02","tid":727400,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T02:59:54.000Z","msg":"一個美國經濟 = 全個歐洲 + 加國 + 墨西哥<br />\n班傻系點解會覺得自己夠玩？"},{"pid":"094bd30e36dfd54ea5ec312a528f251c7b4775d6","tid":727400,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T04:18:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}